SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT PRD004.EXT_CAT , PRD004.PLN_CD , PRD004.MTOCD , PRD004.PLN_MY , SUM (PRD004.PLN_RES) , PRD001.MTONAM , PRD001.CTEGRY FROM PRD004 , PRD001 WHERE ':1' <= SUBSTR ( PRD004.PLN_MY , 1 , 6) AND SUBSTR ( PRD004.PLN_MY , 1 , 6) < ':2' AND PRD001.MTOCD = PRD004.MTOCD GROUP BY PRD004.EXT_CAT , PRD004.PLN_CD , PRD001.CTEGRY , PRD004.MTOCD , PRD001.MTONAM , PRD004.PLN_MY
